        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p> <strong>Athlete Opportunity and Taxpayer Integrity Act </strong></p> <p>This bill denies a tax deduction for contributions (except contributions made directly to certain institutions of higher education) used to compensate one or more secondary or post-secondary school athletes for the use of their names, images, or likenesses by reason of their status as athletes.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
